_sText:
This is a map with a giant volcano in the middle and many lush plants around. And yo top it off with all the foliage around, fog will make your hiding spots even sneakier. I hope you all enjoy.

Features: 
-Bombsite on top of the smoky volcano
-Foggy weather

Install:
Extract the map file (de_volcano_gpk.bsp), and the navigation file to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps).

Author: GabrielPapaK

Time: 4 Hours

Hope you enjoy!
